  review result-handling rules (codex-result-handling skill): do not
  auto-apply fixes from a review, preserve evidence boundaries. Adapted
  into skills/autoresearch/references/codex-integration.md.
  https://github.com/openai/codex-plugin-cc

- Cursor team-kit `thermo-nuclear-code-quality-review`
  (https://github.com/cursor/plugins, commit 3347cba) — the
  implementation-quality / maintainability review substance (the
  PR-review ceremony stripped), used as the Tier 3 advisory pass in
  skills/accept/roles/quality-review.md. See the upstream repository for
  its license terms.

Reference (NOT carried in this codebase): openai/codex (Apache 2.0)
ships a /goal command at codex-rs/core/templates/goals/ with the same
architecture as Claude Code's native /goal. This plugin defers loop
execution to whichever /goal is built into Claude Code, and does not
duplicate that prose.

